      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">26.202</ph> Local area preference.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1702e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  <ph rev="FAC 2019-02 June 5, 2019" class="- topic/ph "> When<?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2017-009?><?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 26.202 by designating the undesignated paragraph as paragraph (a) and?></ph> awarding
emergency response contracts during the term of a major disaster
or emergency declaration by the President of the United States under
the authority of the Robert T. Stafford Disaster Relief and Emergency
Assistance Act (<ph class="- topic/ph ">
                     <xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/browse.xhtml;jsessionid=114A3287C7B3359E597506A31FC855B3"
                           format="html"
                           scope="external"
                           class="- topic/xref ">42 U.S.C. 5121</xref>
                  </ph>, <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">et
seq</i>.), preference shall be given, to the extent feasible and
practicable, to local firms. Preference may be given through a local
area set-aside or an evaluation preference.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1702e40" rev="FAC 2019-02 June 5, 2019" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                   When using the <?FM MARKER [Why] adding paragraph (b).?>authority
under the Stafford Act, see the definitions of “micro-purchase threshold”
and “simplified acquisition threshold” in <xref href="FAR-i1125359.dita#i1125359"
                        base="i1125359"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">2.101</xref> for the authority
to use an increased micro-purchase threshold and simplified acquisition threshold.<?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2017-009?></p>
            </li>
